Open up the Health app on your iPhone, then tap the *Health Data* tab at the
bottom, tap *List* at the top, then tap on *All* (the first item in that list).
It gives you a list of categories you have logged some health data against.
And, sure enough, on the top right hand corner, there’s that share button. I
was curious, so I tapped it to see what happens. It popped up with a wee
message, elucidating slightly:

